- Self-sufficient crafting and repair of essential tools
{% endblock %}

{% block speech_style %}Speaks with a strong Nord accent and blunt, economical phrasing. Uses practical farming metaphors and weather references. Delivery is matter-of-fact and straightforward. Tone is gruff but honest, with occasional dry observations about life's hardships. Speech patterns reflect isolation, with abrupt transitions and limited social niceties.{% endblock %}